Managers learn to spot opportunities to increase customer satisfaction through speed , and shift some responsibility for analyzing , improving and streamlining work processes from themselves to teams of employees . 
Every morning , tractor-trailer trucks arrive at the Natick Ground Station from Boston 's Logan Airport , carrying the day 's package load . In peak periods that load may include 4,000 pieces . The packages must be sorted quickly and distributed to smaller vans for delivery , so couriers can be on the road by 8:35 . 
